{"tid":1116733,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"多名參加水上活動人士在狂風暴雨下未能返回岸邊","createTime":"2019-04-20T07:58:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-20T08:09:49.000Z","uid":240362,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"f9a558e8c273ced863e040cd073cd76d05d8e473","tid":1116733,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T07:58:26.000Z","msg":"在暴雨及雷暴警告下，兩男一女在將軍澳工業邨對開海面玩滑浪風帆期間，未能返回岸邊；六名在西貢碼頭對開玩獨木舟的人士，亦未能埋岸，消防及水警正前往協助。另外，兩名在東龍島對開魚排工作的男女，在狂風下墮海，正等待救援。"},{"pid":"a5504e4ff7ada86f4a303a6ae28c8f74018e7cc7","tid":1116733,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T08:05:29.000Z","msg":"抵死<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1104a35f56a7ac143d7edfdf3c17ddd195bfde4","tid":1116733,"uid":69746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T08:09:28.000Z","msg":"由佢死啦 個腦都壞左 救番都無用<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3aba0d9ac69df0662099090758d1f941c5480a59","tid":1116733,"uid":129622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T08:09:49.000Z","msg":"無咩好抵死 最後都係有班人冒險救佢地<br />\n玩水班友救唔返就抵死喇"}]}